plot: Frank, Heiko and Patricia go on a Sunday-Trip. Tina stays at home, she doesn't have her jealousy of Frank's new girlfriend under control. Elke meets Döring again, but doesn't let him go too far. She hopes to marry him in a few months. Peter visits Mrs. Meinhart. They come to terms with each other, and the teacher promises to help her former student find a job. At Ullrichs, the house blessing has been restored. Tina and Patricia get along well. Denise bursts into the cozy atmosphere. She asks Frank to abort her child.
